<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Email Verified - Prof Bioresearch</title>
</head>

<body
    style="margin:0; padding:0; background-color:#f4f6f9; color:#333; font-family:'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased; -moz-osx-font-smoothing:grayscale;">

    <div
        style="max-width:600px; margin:40px auto; background-color:#ffffff; padding:30px; border-radius:10px; box-shadow:0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">

        <!-- Header -->
        <div style="text-align:center; padding-bottom:20px;">
            <h1 style="margin:0; font-size:26px; font-weight:700; color:#0056b3;">
                Email Verified ✔
            </h1>
        </div>

        <!-- Body -->
        <div style="font-size:16px; line-height:1.6; color:#444;">
            <p>Dear <strong>{{firstName}} {{lastName}}</strong>,</p>
            <p>We’re pleased to inform you that your email address has been <strong>successfully verified</strong>.</p>
            <p>Your employee account is now fully active, and you can securely access the <strong>Prof
                    Bioresearch</strong> systems and resources.</p>

            <p><strong>Next steps:</strong></p>
            <ul style="margin:0 0 1rem 20px; padding:0; color:#444;">
                <li>Log in using your employee credentials</li>
                <li>Update your profile information if needed</li>
                <li>Review company policies and IT guidelines</li>
            </ul>

            <p>If you encounter any issues accessing your account, please contact the IT support team for assistance.
            </p>

            <p>Best regards,<br /><strong>The Prof Bioresearch IT Team</strong></p>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div
            style="margin-top:40px; font-size:12px; color:#777; text-align:center; border-top:1px solid #e6e9ef; padding-top:20px;">
            &copy; {{year}} Prof Bioresearch · All rights reserved<br />
            <a href="https://www.profbioresearch.com"
                style="color:#0056b3; text-decoration:none;">www.profbioresearch.com</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>